      <title>如何正确查看BOLL布林指标 --知识铺</title>
      <link>https://index.zshipu.com/stocktactics/post/20240413/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8BBOLL%E5%B8%83%E6%9E%97%E6%8C%87%E6%A0%87--%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E9%93%BA/</link>
